#KLWP Theme 

#Make sure before installing this theme first install klwp pro, because this theme can not stand alone. 
#For now this theme does not support 18: 9 screen like LGG6 / note8 / s8. 

#Features 
Music 
Weather 
News 
Navbar(on/off)

LGG6 / note8 / S8 같은 : 9 화면 #For 지금이 주제는 18를 지원하지 않습니다.
